                    <span>This film of the Killer Wave should be viewed by many people to understand the powers that are shared by the Tsunami before one day it's to late and you become a victim of Mother Natures worst and most fatal disaster.Hearing about it's power,speed,and distruction means nothing.You have to See it to Believe it.</span>
                  
              
